data.description: Welcome to your stunning custom home on 5.28 private acres less than 1 mile from Serenbe Farms! This property has it all and more - large chef's kitchen with granite countertops and massive walk-in butler's pantry you can stock up from the garden and greenhouse, 12+ seat dining room, and wide open porches and decks around the entire home for entertaining or enjoying the expansive property. Plus dedicated wired workshops! Inside you are welcomed by soaring ceilings, hardwood floors, and spacious, well appointed rooms. The main level boasts a living room, den/flex space, enclosed sunporch that is currently being used as a gym, and 2 guest rooms. The Primary suite upstairs has a large separate sitting room/office and en-suite bath with double vanities, tile shower, and soaking tub. This property is a rare find - don't miss this opportunity to make this custom home yours!
